data.description: Updated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in a quiet cul-de-sac. This house has a large utility/laundry room and an open floor plan. New flooring throughout the living room, dining room, kitchen, and hallway. Fresh paint in most of the house. The stove, microwave, dishwasher, washer and dryer hook-up. Large backyard with privacy fence. Master bedroom and Bedroom 2 both have large walk-in closets.
